%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bridge%20Missed%201-Year%20Deadline%20In%202017.%207%20Years%20On%2C%20Falls%20In%20Strong%20Winds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20portion%20of%20an%20under-construction%20bridge%20in%20Telangana's%20Peddapalli%20district%20collapsed%20on%20Monday%20night.%20Two%20concrete%20girders%2C%20out%20of%20five%20between%20two%20pillars%20about%20100%20feet%20apart%2C%20collapsed%20around%209.45%20pm%20after%20a%20strong%20wind%20blew%20in%20the%20area.%20Locals%20apprehend%20the%20other%20three%20may%20give%20way%20soon%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLuckily%2C%20a%20marriage%20party%20of%2065%20people%20on%20a%20bus%20passed%20by%20just%20one%20minute%20earlier%20and%20escaped%20being%20crushed%20by%20the%20concrete%2C%26quot%3B%20Sirikonda%20Bakka%20Rao%2C%20who%20was%20sarpanch%20of%20Odedu%20village%20-%20600%20metres%20away%2C%20till%20his%20term%20lapsed%20two%20months%20ago%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nearly%20one-kilometre%20bridge%20across%20the%20Manair%20river%20was%20inaugurated%20by%20the%20then%20Telangana%20assembly%20Speaker%20S%20Madhusudhana%20Chary%20and%20local%20MLA%20Putta%20Madhu%20in%202016%20and%20nearly%20Rs%2049%20crore%20was%20sanctioned%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20completed%20in%20a%20year%20and%20was%20meant%20to%20reduce%20the%20distance%20between%20three%20towns%20-%20Manthani%2C%20Parakal%20and%20Jammikunta%20by%20about%2050%20km.%20The%20bridge%20was%20to%20connect%20Garmillapallu%20in%20Tekumatla%20mandal%20in%20Bhupalpalli%20to%20Odededu%20in%20Peddapalli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contractor%20had%20reportedly%20stopped%20the%20work%20within%20a%20year%20or%20two%20as%20he%20was%20under%20pressure%20for%20commissions%20and%20the%20government%20was%20not%20paying%20out%20his%20dues%2C%20locals%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20contractor%20had%20built%20a%20bridge%20in%20Vemulawada%20that%20was%20washed%20away%20during%20heavy%20rain%20in%202021%2C%20Mr%20Rao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20villagers%20had%20been%20using%20the%20same%20route%2C%20laying%20a%20mud%20road%20under%20the%20bridge%2C%20for%20the%20last%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cost%20of%20the%20project%20was%20escalated%20and%20last%20year%20another%20Rs%2011%20crore%20was%20added%20to%20the%20estimatd%20cost%20without%20even%2060%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20work%20being%20completed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sandeep%20Rao%2C%20a%20local.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713871380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fleq3hj5c_telangana-bridge_625x300_23_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2Funder-construction-telangana-bridge-collapses-due-to-strong-winds-5505229%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20portion%20of%20an%20under-construction%20bridge%20in%20Telangana's%20Peddapalli%20district%20collapsed%20on%20Monday%20night.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2Funder-construction-telangana-bridge-collapses-due-to-strong-winds-5505229%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2Funder-construction-telangana-bridge-collapses-due-to-strong-winds-5505229%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2Funder-construction-telangana-bridge-collapses-due-to-strong-winds-5505229%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cate%20Blanchett%2C%20Colin%20Farrell%2C%20Jessica%20Chastain%20Voice%20Projects%20in%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%20Immersive%20Lineup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713871305000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fcannes-immersive.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D562%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235979128%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival%