0Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR)%20had%20earlier%20said%2C%20former%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Kamal%20Nath's%20son%20Nakul%20Nath%20topped%20the%20richest%20contestants%20list%20in%20the%20Phase-I%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20held%20on%20April%2019%2C%20with%20nearly%20Rs%20717%20crore%20worth%20of%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandra%20Sekhar's%20family%20has%20a%20liability%20of%20Rs%201%2C138%20crore%20to%20JP%20Morgan%20Chase%20Bank%20of%20USA%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Line%20of%20Credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Burripalem%20village%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20to%20working%20as%20physician%20teacher%20at%20Johns%20Hopkins%20University%20-%20Sinai%20Hospital%20to%20founding%20UWorld%20(online%20learning%20and%20study%20resources%20platform)%2C%20Chandra%20Sekhar's%20journey%20has%20been%20fascinating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Doctor-Entrepreneur-Politician%20completed%20his%20MBBS%20at%20NTR%20University%20of%20Health%20Sciences%20Vijayawada%20in%201999%20and%20pursued%20MD%20(Internal%20Medicine)%20from%20Geisinger%20Medical%20Center%20in%20Danville%2C%20Pennsylvania%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20secured%2027th%20rank%20among%2060%2C000%20students%20who%20took%20the%20EAMCET%20medical%20entrance%20examination%20(MBBS)%20in%20the%20state%20which%20was%20considered%20the%20most%20competitive%20examination%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandra%20Sekhar%20with%20an%20interest%20in%20public%20service%2C%20has%20been%20working%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20TDP's%20NRI%20wing%20since%202010%20to%20support%20several%20welfare%20programmes%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20desired%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20from%20Narasaraopet%20segment%20in%202014%2C%20TDP%20allotted%20the%20ticket%20to%20R%20Sambasiva%20Rao%20due%20to%20political%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20filing%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20he%20declared%20Rs%20605.57%20crore%20as%20per%20US%20Tax%20Cycle%20Year%20January%202022%20to%20December%202022%20in%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20investments%20and%20shares%20in%20several%20US-based%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20possesses%20luxury%20cars%20such%20as%20Rolls%20Royce%20Ghost%2C%20Mercedes%20Benz%20and%20Tesla%20in%20the%20USA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChnadra%20Sekhar%20will%20take%20on%20YSR%20Congress%20Party's%20K%20Venkata%20Rosaiah%20in%20the%20elections.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713871140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fs9qg2r6o_pemmasani-chandra-sekhar_625x300_22_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwith-rs-5-785-crore-assets-this-lok-sabha-contestant-is-wealthiest-so-far-5504033%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TDP's%20candidate%20for%20Guntur%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20P%20Chandra%20Sekhar%20has%20captured%20headlines%20after%20he%20declared%20his%20family%20assets%20-%20both%20movable%20and%20immovable%20-%20at%20Rs%205%2C785%20crore%2C%20in%20his%20election%20affidavit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwith-rs-5-785-crore-assets-this-lok-sabha-contestant-is-wealthiest-so-far-5504033%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwith-rs-5-785-crore-assets-this-lok-sabha-contestant-is-wealthiest-so-far-5504033%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwith-rs-5-785-crore-assets-this-lok-sabha-contestant-is-wealthiest-so-far-5504033%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Voyager%201%20Sends%20Info%20To%20Earth%20After%20Months%20From%2015%20Billion%20Miles%20Away%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENASA's%20Voyager%201%20probe%20--%20the%20most%20distant%20man-made%20object%20in%20the%20universe%20--%20is%20returning%20usable%20information%20to%20ground%20control%20following%20months%20of%20spouting%20gibberish%2C%20the%20US%20space%20agency%20announced%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spaceship%20stopped%20sending%20readable%20data%20back%20to%20Earth%20on%20November%2014%2C%202023%2C%20even%20though%20controllers%20could%20tell%20it%20was%20still%20receiving%20their%20commands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20teams%20working%20at%20NASA's%20Jet%20Propulsion%20Laboratory%20discovered%20that%20a%20single%20malfunctioning%20chip%20was%20to%20blame%2C%20and%20devised%20a%20clever%20coding%20fix%20that%20worked%20within%20the%20tight%20memory%20constraints%20of%20its%2046-year-old%20computer%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVoyager%201%20spacecraft%20is%20returning%20usable%20data%20about%20the%20health%20and%20status%20of%20its%20onboard%20engineering%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHi%2C%20it's%20me.%20-%20V1%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FjgGFBfxIOe%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FjgGFBfxIOe%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20NASA%20Voyager%20(%40NASAVoyager)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNASAVoyager%2Fstatus%2F1782454547446890633%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20next%20step%20is%20to%20enable%20the%20spacecraft%20to%20begin%20returning%20science%20data%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%201977%2C%20Voyager%201%20was%20mankind's%20first%20spacecraft%20to%20enter%20the%20interstellar%20medium%2C%20in%202012%2C%20and%20is%20currently%20more%20than%2015%20billion%20miles%20from%20Earth.%20Messages%20sent%20from%20Earth%20take%20about%2022.5%20hours%20to%20reach%20the%20spacecraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20twin%2C%20Voyager%202%2C%20also%20left%20the%20