Minutes%20Before%20Onset%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EResearchers%20have%20developed%20a%20new%20AI-based%20model%20that%20can%20predict%20irregular%20heartbeat%2C%20or%20cardiac%20arrhythmia%2C%20about%2030%20minutes%20before%20its%20onset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20found%20that%20the%20model%20proved%20to%20be%2080%20per%20cent%20accurate%20in%20predicting%20the%20transition%20from%20a%20normal%20cardiac%20rhythm%20to%20atrial%20fibrillation%2C%20the%20most%20common%20type%20of%20cardiac%20arrhythmia%20in%20which%20the%20heart's%20upper%20chambers%20(atria)%20beat%20irregularly%20and%20are%20out%20of%20sync%20with%20the%20lower%20ones%20(ventricles).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%2C%20including%20researchers%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Luxembourg%2C%20said%20that%20their%20AI-model%2C%20which%20gives%20early%20warnings%2C%20could%20be%20easily%20installed%20in%20smartphones%20to%20process%20the%20data%20recorded%20on%20smartwatches.%20The%20warnings%20could%20allow%20patients%20to%20take%20preventive%20measures%20to%20keep%20their%20cardiac%20rhythm%20stable%2C%20they%20said.%20The%20study%20is%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20Patterns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20developing%20the%20model%2C%20the%20team%20trained%20it%20on%2024%20hour-long%20recordings%20gathered%20from%20350%20patients%20at%20Tongji%20Hospital%20in%20Wuhan%2C%20China.%20The%20model%2C%20that%20the%20researchers%20have%20named%20WARN%20(Warning%20of%20Atrial%20fibRillatioN)%2C%20is%20based%20on%20deep-learning%2C%20a%20type%20of%20machine-learning%20AI%20algorithms%20that%20learn%20patterns%20from%20past%20data%20to%20make%20predictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeep-learning%20is%20more%20specialised%20as%20it%20has%20multiple%20layers%20in%20its%20decision-making%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20found%20that%20WARN%20gave%20early%20warnings%2C%20on%20average%2030%20minutes%20before%20the%20start%20of%20atrial%20fibrillation%2C%20and%20is%20the%20first%20method%20to%20provide%20a%20warning%20far%20from%20onset%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20used%20heart%20rate%20data%20to%20train%20a%20deep%20learning%20model%20that%20can%20recognise%20different%20phases%20--%20(normal)%20sinus%20rhythm%2C%20pre-atrial%20fibrillation%20and%20atrial%20fibrillation%20--%20and%20calculate%20a%20'probability%20of%20danger'%20that%20the%20patient%20will%20have%20an%20imminent%20episode%2C%26quot%3B%20Jorge%20Goncalves%2C%20from%20the%20Luxembourg%20Centre%20for%20Systems%20Biomedicine%20(LCSB)%2C%20University%20of%20Luxembourg%2C%20and%20the%20study's%20corresponding%20author%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20approaching%20atrial%20fibrillation%2C%20the%20probability%20increases%20until%20it%20crosses%20a%20specific%20threshold%2C%20providing%20an%20early%20warning%2C%20Goncalves%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20of%20low%20computational%20cost%2C%20the%20AI-model%20is%20%26quot%3Bideal%20for%20integration%20into%20wearable%20technologies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20researchers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20devices%20can%20be%20used%20by%20patients%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20so%20our%20results%20open%20possibilities%20for%20the%20development%20of%20real-time%20monitoring%20and%20early%20warnings%20from%20comfortable%20wearable%20devices%2C%26quot%3B%20study%20author%20Arthur%20Montanari%2C%20an%20LCSB%20researcher%2C%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713870240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Forhm5fbg_heart-rate-generic-cardiac-monitor-generic-hospital-generic-pixabay_625x300_23_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fai-model-developed-to-predict-cardiac-irregularity-30-minutes-before-onset-study-5504434%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2