%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20came%20to%20Rajasthan%20the%20day%20before%20yesterday%2C%20I%20had%20presented%20some%20truths%20before%20the%20country%20in%20my%2090-second%20speech.%20This%20has%20created%20panic%20in%20the%20entire%20Congress%20and%20INDI%20alliance.%20I%20had%20put%20the%20truth%20before%20the%20country%20that%20Congress%20is%20hatching%20a%20deep%20conspiracy%20to%20snatch%20your%20property%20and%20distribute%20it%20to%20its%20special%20people.%20I%20exposed%20their%20vote%20bank%20and%20appeasement%20politics.%20After%20all%2C%20why%20is%20Congress%20so%20afraid%20of%20the%20truth%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20asked%20what%20would%20have%20happened%20if%20there%20was%20a%20Congress%20government%20at%20the%20centre%20after%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202014%2C%20you%20allowed%20Modi%20to%20serve%20in%20Delhi.%20Then%20the%20country%20made%20decisions%20that%20no%20one%20had%20even%20imagined.%20But%20think%20about%20what%20would%20have%20happened%20even%20after%202014%20and%20even%20today%20if%20there%20was%20a%20Congress%20government%20in%20Delhi.%20Had%20Congress%20been%20there%2C%20stones%20would%20have%20been%20pelted%20at%20our%20forces%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20even%20today.%20Had%20Congress%20been%20there%2C%20the%20enemies%20would%20have%20come%20from%20across%20the%20border.%20Had%20Congress%20been%20there%2C%20neither%20One%20Rank%20One%20Pension%20would%20have%20been%20implemented%20for%20our%20soldiers%20nor%20would%20our%20ex-servicemen%20have%20received%20Rs%201%20lakh%20crore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20sharpening%20his%20attacks%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20that%20the%20thinking%20of%20Congress%20has%20always%20been%20of%20appeasement%20and%20vote%20bank%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20the%20Congress%20government%20was%20formed%20at%20the%20Centre%20in%202004%2C%20its%20first%20task%20was%20to%20reduce%20the%20reservation%20for%20SC%2FST%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20give%20reservation%20to%20Muslims.%20This%20was%20a%20pilot%20project%2C%20which%20Congress%20wanted%20to%20try%20in%20the%20entire%20country.%20Between%202004%20and%202010%2C%20Congress%20tried%20to%20implement%20Muslim%20reservations%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20four%20times.%20But%20due%20to%20legal%20hurdles%20and%20the%20awareness%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20it%20could%20not%20fulfil%20its%20plans%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Constitution%20is%20completely%20against%20it.%20The%20right%20of%20reservation%20which%20Baba%20Saheb%20gave%20to%20Dalits%2C%20backward%20classes%20and%20tribals%2C%20Congress%20and%20INDI%20Alliance%20wanted%20to%20give%20it%20to%20Muslims%20based%20on%20religion.%20Amidst%20these%20conspiracies%20of%20Congress%2C%20Modi%20is%20today%20guaranteeing%20you%20from%20an%20open%20platform%20that%20reservations%20for%20Dalits%2C%20backward%20classes%20and%20tribals%20will%20neither%20be%20ended%20nor%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20be%20divided%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion.%20This%20is%20Modi's%20guarantee%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713869400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F3drvci2o_pm-modi-1200-_625x300_23_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmy-90-second-speech-created-panic-in-congress-india-bloc-pm-modi-5503549%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20a%20debate%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20remarks%20that%20%26quot%3BCongress%20wants%20to%20snatch%20women's%20Mangalsutra%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20reiterated%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20had%20put%20the%20truth%20before%20the%20country%20that%20Congress%20is%20hatching%20