ims%20to%20stop%20bringing%20the%20snakes%20in%20with%20them%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20doctor%20holds%20a%20snake%20in%20a%20stock%20image.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662773e00dfb1341e9fdd369%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20stock%20image%20shows%20a%20doctor%20holding%20a%20snake.%3Cp%3EiStock%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20Australian%20hospital%20is%20asking%20snakebite%20victims%20to%20stop%20bringing%20the%20snakes%20to%20the%20ER.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20hospital's%20director%20said%20that%20having%20a%20live%20snake%20in%20the%20ER%20puts%20staff%20and%20patients%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20it%20also%20delays%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20for%20patients%20to%20get%20treated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20hospital%20in%20Australia%20is%20asking%20snakebite%20victims%20not%20to%20bring%20the%20reptiles%20with%20them%20to%20the%20emergency%20room%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2024-04-22%2Fbite-victims-warned-stop-bringing-snakes-to-emergency-department%2F103752506%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAustralian%20Broadcasting%20Corporation%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20instance%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20staff%20at%20Bundaberg%20Hospital%20in%20Queensland%20were%20handed%20a%20plastic%20container%20with%20a%20small%20Eastern%20Brown%20snake%20inside%2C%20according%20to%20the%20news%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20snake%20species%20is%20common%20across%20much%20of%20eastern%20Australia%2C%20and%20its%20deadly%20venom%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Faustralia-news%2F2024%2Fmar%2F20%2Fnorth-queensland-snake-bite-death-deeragun-townsville-hospital%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAbout%25203%252C000%2520snake%2520bites%2520are%2Caccording%2520to%2520a%2520nationwide%2520review.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecountry's%20most%20common%20cause%20of%20fatal%20snake%20bites.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Faustralia-news%2F2024%2Fmar%2F20%2Fnorth-queensland-snake-bite-death-deeragun-townsville-hospital%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAbout%25203%252C000%2520snake%2520bites%2520are%2Caccording%2520to%2520a%2520nationwide%2520review.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20about%203%2C000%20snakebites%20are%20reported%20in%20Australia%20each%20year%2C%20with%2041%25%20coming%20from%20Eastern%20Brown%20snakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported%20that%20one%20of%20these%20snakes%20caused%20a%20man's%20death%20after%20he%20was%20bitten%20multiple%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bundaberg%20Hospital's%20director%20of%20emergency%20medicine%2C%20Adam%20Michael%2C%20the%20snake%20at%20his%20hospital%20this%20month%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20very%20well%20secured.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20trying%20to%20escape%20the%20plastic%20container%2C%20ABC%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20staff%20got%20a%20fright%20and%20the%20serious%20consequence%20of%20that%20is%20it%20delays%20people's%20time%20to%20treatment%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20told%20the%20news%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20people%20to%20be%20able%20to%20get%20seen%20and%20assessed%20quickly%2C%20and%20having%20a%20live%20snake%20in%20the%20department%20slows%20up%20that%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20snake%20catcher%20told%20the%20news%20outlet%20that%20he%20had%20removed%20several%20snakes%20bought%20into%20the%20hospital%2C%20many%20arriving%20in%20plastic%20containers%20or%20bags.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Australian%20Medical%20Association%2C%20wait%20times%20in%20Australia%20for%20emergency%20rooms%20are%20at%20their%20longest%20in%20a%20decade%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.9news.com.au%2Fnational%2Faustralian-surgery-wait-times-longest-ever-emergency-rooms-strangled-ama-report-finds%2F648102d5-0c6a-437b-adcf-5fa6a387c780%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E9%20News%20reported%20last%20week.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20people%20bringing%20in%20snakes%20may%20think%20it%20will%20help%20doctors%20with%20identification%20and%20speed%20up%20getting%20the%20right%20treatment%2C%20Michael%20told%20ABC%20that%20all%20it%20does%20is%20endanger%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20doctors%20aren't%20trained%20to%20identify%20snakes%2C%20so%20it%20only%20%26quot%3Bputs%20the%20staff%20at%20risk%20as%20well%20as%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20ABC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBringing%20in%20the%20snakes%2C%20he%20added%2C%20risks%20becoming%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%26quot%3B%20disaster%20with%20no%20upside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20determine%20if%20you%20need%20anti-venom%20and%2C%20if%20so%2C%20what%20anti-venom%20you%20need%20based%20on%20clinical%20signs%2C%20blood%20tests%2C%20and%20also%20the%20snake%20venom%20detection%20kits%20that%20we%20keep%20here%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustralia-hospital-warns-snakebite-victims-leave-snakes-at-home-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713868052000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662774110dfb1341e9fdd36b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustralia-hospital-warns-snakebite-victims-leave-snakes-at-home-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Snakebite%20victims%20in%20Australia%20are%20being%20advised%20not%20to%20bring%20the%20snakes%20to%20the%20emergency%20room%2C%20following%20a%20scare%20at%20a%20Queensland%20hospital%20this%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzitser%40businessinsider.com%20(Joshua%20Zitser)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canon