their%20intended%20outcomes%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%20%E2%80%94%20from%20inadequately%20prepared%20managers%20to%20breakdowns%20in%20communication%20between%20managers%20and%20employees%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-early-put-on-performance-improvement-plan-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esubjective%20judgments%20of%20performance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20experience%2C%20the%20primary%20reason%20for%20the%20failure%20of%20PIPs%20lies%20in%20the%20irreparable%20fracture%20they%20create%20in%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20employee%20and%20manager.%20Once%20the%20PIP%20process%20begins%2C%20this%20fracture%20in%20trust%20is%20seldom%20repaired.%20The%20atmosphere%20becomes%20palpably%20tense%2C%20and%20trust%20begins%20to%20erode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPIPs%20lead%20to%20an%20irreparable%20fracture%20in%20the%20relationship%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20stories%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurvived-performance-plan-wasnt-worth-hard-work-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemployees%20feeling%20unfairly%20targeted%20and%20demoralized%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fput-on-pip-fought-back-won-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomplaints%20of%20mishandling%20of%20PIPs%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20illuminated%20the%20complexities%20and%20challenges%20inherent%20in%20performance%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20stories%20serve%20as%20cautionary%20tales%2C%20highlighting%20the%20potential%20pitfalls%20of%20traditional%20PIPs%20and%20the%20need%20for%20organizations%20to%20rethink%20their%20approach%20to%20managing%20underperformance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20an%20employee%20successfully%20meets%20the%20objectives%20outlined%20in%20the%20PIP%2C%20the%20underlying%20tension%20and%20strain%20on%20the%20relationship%20often%20persist%2C%20adversely%20impacting%20productivity%20and%20morale%20not%20only%20for%20the%20manager%20and%20the%20employee%2C%20but%20for%20the%20entire%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20rarely%20seen%20managers%20more%20tense%20than%20when%20addressing%20a%20PIP.%20These%20conditions%20don't%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20a%20productive%20process.%20At%20their%20core%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpip-performance-improvement-plan-how-to-survive-career-development-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPIPs%20should%20reflect%20an%20organization's%20commitment%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20achieving%20high%20performance.%20They%20should%20identify%20areas%20for%20improvement%2C%20set%20clear%20expectations%2C%20and%20provide%20a%20roadmap%20for%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20better%20approach%20involves%20choice%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%201998%20to%202004%2C%20I%20was%20an%20HR%20executive%20at%20Cisco%20Systems%2C%20where%20I%20encountered%20a%20novel%20approach%20to%20the%20traditional%20PIP%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20my%20arrival%2C%20Cisco%20had%20recognized%20that%20something%20was%20broken%20in%20the%20PIP%20process.%20The%20HR%20team%20conducted%20a%20thorough%20analysis%20of%20PIPs%20across%20the%20company%20and%20made%20a%20fascinating%20discovery%3A%20most%20individuals%20placed%20on%20a%20PIP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-hr-performance-improvement-plans-pip-pivot-had-to-quit-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleft%20the%20company%20within%20a%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20their%20performance%20improved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20spoke%20with%20many%20of%20the%20employees%20who%20survived%20their%20PIP%20and%20improved%20their%20performance%20yet%20still%20chose%20to%20leave%2C%20and%20the%20story%20they%20heard%20had%20a%20similar%20refrain.%20The%20employees%20felt%20their%20managers%20did%20not%20really%20support%20them%2C%20they%20no%20longer%20felt%20they%20were%20in%20a%20safe%20work%20environment%2C%20and%20many%20felt%20humiliated%20and%20deeply%20hurt%20by%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20data%20and%20listening%20to%20employees%2C%20the%20HR%20team%20developed%20a%20new%20approach%20that%20involved%20choice.%20Employees%20who%20were%20not%20performing%20to%20an%20acceptable%20level%20were%20offered%20two%20options%3A%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EEnter%20a%20PIP%20and%20try%20to%20improve%2C%20or%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EMutually%20agree%20to%20separate%20from%20the%20company%20and%20receive%20more%20severance%20than%20they%20would%20if%20they%20failed%20the%20PIP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20presenting%20employees%20with%20this%20alternative%20path%2C%20Cisco%20empowered%20them%20to%20make%20decisions%20aligned%20with%20their%20personal%20circumstances.%20This%20approach%20also%20alleviated%20stress%20for%20managers%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20focus%20on%20other%20priorities.%20The%20conversations%20became%20more%20constructive%2C%20and%20employees%20appreciated%20being%20given%20a%20choice%20rather%20than%20feeling%20cornered%20into%20a%20dead-end%20PIP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EChallenge%20conventional%20practices%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20since%20leaving%20Cisco%2C%20I've%20introduced%20this%20alternative%20approach%20to%20other%20organizations%2C%20contributing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-companies-boost-employee-wellbeing-build-healthy-culture-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthier%20cultures%20and%20more%20constructive%20environments%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerformance%20evaluation%20is%20inherently%20subjective%2C%20and%20no%20process%20can%20eliminate%20all%20conflicts%20or%20unexpected%20reactions.%20However%2C%20offering%20employees%20a%20choice%20rather%20than%20a%20one-way%20ticket%20to%20a%20PIP%20can%20lead%20to%20more%20positive%20outcomes%20and%20healthier%20work%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20HR%20professionals%20and%20organizational%20leaders%2C%20it's%20our%20responsibility%20to%20challenge%20conventional%20practices%20and%20explore%20innovative%20solutions.%20By%20rethinking%20performance%20management%20and%20embracing%20alternative%20approaches%2C%20we%20can%20create%20a%20culture%20of%20trust%2C%20transparency%2C%20and%20continuous%20improvement%20where%20both%20employees%20and%20organizations%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESteve%20Cadigan%20is%20a%20talent%20advisor%20to%20leaders%20and%20organizations%20around%20the%20world.%20He%20specializes%20in%20helping%20firms%20build%20talent%20strategies%20for%20the%20modern%20workplace.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperformance-improvement-plan-ruin-relationships-better-alternative-pip-hr-strategy-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713863461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6627229323b29110d301adcc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperformance-improvement-plan-ruin-relationships-better-alternative-pip-hr-strategy-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20HR%20professional%20with%20over%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20shares%20a%20better%20approach%20to%20performance-improvement%20plans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Steve%20Cadigan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperformance-improvement-plan-ruin-relationships-better-alternative-pip-hr-strategy-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SRK%20reacts%20to%20Mohanlal's%20groove%20on%20'Zinda%20Banda'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713863434000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109528229%2Cimgsize-45536.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan