irst%20phase%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-phase-1-voting-bjp-vs-india-bloc-as-india-votes-in-1st-phase-of-lok-sabha-polls-10-points-5472095%5C%22%3ELok%20Sabha%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20marking%20the%20first%20drop%20since%20the%20last%20three%20electoral%20cycles.%20This%20has%20sparked%20concern%20among%20political%20parties%20and%20candidates%20alike%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Felection-commission-of-india-eci-%5C%22%3EElection%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20phase%2C%2093%20out%20of%20102%20constituencies%20witnessed%20a%20decline%20in%20turnout%20compared%20to%202019.%20Of%20the%2040%20seats%20won%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fbjp%5C%22%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20that%20year%2C%20as%20many%20as%2039%20saw%20a%20drop%20in%20turnout%2C%20while%20among%20the%2015%20seats%20won%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%2012%20saw%20a%20reduced%20voting%20percentage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20ECI%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20taken%20measures%20to%20address%20this%20decline%2C%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-pm-modi-asks-people-to-vote-in-record-numbers-5473883%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20urging%20citizens%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20regardless%20of%20party%20affiliations%2C%20to%20actively%20participate%20in%20what%20is%20known%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fover-97-crore-voters-in-2024-lok-sabha-elections-worlds-largest-5249885%5C%22%3Eworld's%20largest%20democratic%20exercise.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETurnout%20And%20Results%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarious%20theories%20have%20been%20proposed%20to%20explain%20this%20trend%2C%20but%20it%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20there%20is%20no%20strong%20correlation%20between%20turnout%20and%20electoral%20outcomes.%20An%20analysis%20spanning%2016%20elections%20from%201957%20to%202019%20reveals%20that%20turnout%20increased%2010%20times%2C%20with%20governments%20getting%20re-elected%20six%20times.%20Conversely%2C%20there%20were%20six%20instances%20of%20turnout%20decline%2C%20with%20governments%20being%20re-elected%20twice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20significant%20factor%20contributing%20to%20the%20low%20turnout%2C%20amidst%20awareness%20campaigns%2C%20is%20the%20prevalence%20of%20heatwaves%20and%20high%20temperatures%20across%20the%20country.%20India's%20average%20temperature%20has%20risen%20by%20approximately%200.7%C2%B0C%20over%20the%20long-term%20average%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20from%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%20released%20on%20August%202%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20study%20conducted%20by%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Kharagpur%2C%20titled%20Surface%20Temperature%20Increase%20over%20India%20during%201980-2020%20and%20Future%20Projections%3A%20Causal%20Relationships%20Between%20Drivers%20and%20Trends%2C%20predicts%20a%20potential%20surge%20of%201.1%20to%205.1%C2%B0C%20in%20India's%20surface%20temperature%20by%202100.%20The%20study%20highlights%20a%20trend%20of%20rising%20temperatures%20during%20both%20pre-monsoon%20and%20post-monsoon%20seasons%20in%20several%20regions%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMercury%20Rising%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202024%2C%20the%20average%20temperature%20reached%2013.14%C2%B0C%2C%20the%20highest%20ever%20recorded%20for%20that%20month%2C%20surpassing%20the%20previous%20record%20set%20in%202020.%20Similarly%2C%20February%202024%20saw%20an%20average%20temperature%20of%2013.54%C2%B0C%2C%20the%20highest%20ever%20for%20February%2C%20breaking%20the%202016%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20study%20based%20on%20data%20from%20the%20Indian%20Meteorological%20Department%20shows%20that%20during%20the%20campaign%20period%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20approximately%2072%25%20of%20constituencies%20could%20experience%20maximum%20temperatures%20of%2035%C2%B0C%20or%20higher.%20Notably%2C%2059%20seats%20may%20face%20temperatures%20between%2040-42%C2%B0C%2C%20while%20194%20seats%20could%20see%20temperatures%20ranging%20from%2037.5-40%C2%B0C.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20analysis%20of%2010%20constituencies%20across%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal%20underscores%20the%20impact%20of%20rising%20temperatures%20on%20voter%20turnout.%20A%20comparison%20of%20temperatures%20on%20polling%20day%20in%20April%202024%20with%20those%20from%20April%202019%20reveals%20an%20upward%20rise%20ranging%20from%201%C2%B0%20to%207%C2%B0C.%20Consequently%2C%20these%20constituencies%20experienced%20a%20decline%20in%20turnout%2C%20ranging%20from%202%25%20to%209%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20essential%20to%20recognise%20that%20other%20factors%2C%20such%20as%20lack%20of%20enthusiasm%20among%20voters%2C%20caste%2Fcommunity%20discontent%2C%20lower%20turnout%20among%20first-time%20voters%2C%20migrant%20populations%2C%20also%20contribute%20to%20the%20overall%20turnout.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20should%20contemplate%20measures%20such%20as%20extending%20voting%20hours%20and%20exploring%20the%20possibility%20of%20secure%20online%20voting%20through%20Aadhar%2FOTPs%20for%20future%20elections%20to%20address%20these%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713861360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fh67b5c8_manipur-repolling_625x300_22_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%