lic%20of%20Ireland%20and%20Cyprus.%20It%20includes%20countries%20such%20as%20Belgium%2C%20France%2C%20Germany%2C%20Italy%2C%20and%20Spain%2C%20along%20with%20Iceland%2C%20Liechtenstein%2C%20Norway%2C%20and%20Switzerland.%20This%20extensive%20area%20not%20only%20offers%20diverse%20cultural%20experiences%20but%20also%20facilitates%20seamless%20travel%20across%20borders%20for%20visa%20holders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Schengen%20visa%20permits%20a%20brief%20stay%20of%20up%20to%2090%20days%20within%20a%20180-day%20timeframe.%20This%20visa%20may%20be%20issued%20as%20either%20a%20single-entry%2C%20enabling%20one%20entry%20into%20the%20Schengen%20area%2C%20or%20a%20multiple-entry%2C%20allowing%20multiple%20visits%20for%20the%20duration%20of%20its%20validity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20The%20New%20Rules%20Affect%20Indians%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20regulations%2C%20Indian%20travellers%20can%20now%20obtain%20a%20two-year%20Schengen%20visa%2C%20a%20marked%20improvement%20from%20the%20shorter%20validity%20periods%20previously%20available.%20To%20qualify%20for%20this%20extended%20two-year%20visa%2C%20applicants%20must%20have%20acquired%20and%20appropriately%20utilised%20two%20Schengen%20visas%20within%20the%20preceding%20three%20years.%20Upon%20successful%20utilisation%20of%20the%20two-year%20visa%2C%20travellers%20can%20typically%20expect%20to%20be%20eligible%20for%20a%20five-year%20Schengen%20visa%2C%20provided%20their%20passport%20maintains%20sufficient%20validity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20rules%20essentially%20say%20that%20Indian%20travellers%20can%20move%20freely%20within%20the%20Schengen%20member%20countries%20for%20short%20stays%2C%20typically%20up%20to%2090%20days%20within%20any%20180-day%20period%2C%20without%20the%20need%20for%20additional%20permits%20or%20authorisations.%20Under%20this%20system%2C%20eligible%20travellers%20with%20a%20proven%20track%20record%20of%20travel%20will%20have%20simplified%20access%20to%20visas%20with%20extended%20validity%2C%20provided%20their%20passport's%20validity%20permits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Cascade'%20system%2C%20as%20it's%20termed%2C%20is%20designed%20to%20reward%20frequent%20travellers%20with%20progressively%20longer%20visa%20durations.%20It%20begins%20with%20a%20two-year%20visa%2C%20and%20upon%20successful%20use%2C%20travellers%20can%20potentially%20qualify%20for%20a%20five-year%20visa.%20While%20these%20visas%20do%20not%20restrict%20the%20purpose%20of%20travel%2C%20they%20do%20not%20allow%20the%20right%20to%20work%20within%20the%20Schengen%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20tweak%20the%20rules%20comes%20in%20the%20broader%20context%20of%20improving%20relations%20between%20the%20EU%20and%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713860580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fth2ilek8_passport-visa-generic-_625x300_23_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-what-is-schengen-visa-and-how-the-new-rules-affect-indians-5503987%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20new%20system%20offers%20substantial%20advantages%20to%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20allowing%20them%20access%20to%20long-term%2C%20multi-entry%20Schengen%20visas%2C%20which%20can%20significantly%20streamline%20travel%20plans%20for%20those%20venturing%20into%20the%20Schengen.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-what-is-schengen-visa-and-how-the-new-rules-affect-indians-5503987%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-what-is-schengen-visa-and-how-the-new-rules-affect-indians-5503987%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-what-is-schengen-visa-and-how-the-new-rules-affect-indians-5503987%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Anushka%20Sharma%20teased%20Virat%20Kohli%22%2C%22content%22%3A%2