mangoes%2C%20watching%20as%20they%20bobbed%20and%20danced.%20The%20wait%20felt%20endless.%20Finally%2C%20after%20what%20seemed%20like%20ages%2C%20peeling%20the%20mango%20and%20devouring%20its%20sweetness%20was%20the%20true%20definition%20of%20bliss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20more%20than%20a%20thousand%20varieties%20of%20mangoes%20grown%20across%20the%20world%2C%20there%20is%20a%20chance%20that%20only%20a%20few%20might%20get%20to%20try%20them%20all.%20However%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20has%20collected%20a%20list%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20expensive%20mangoes%20that%20have%20nothing%20%3Cem%3Eaam%20%3C%2Fem%3E(ordinary)%20about%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Sindhri%20Mango%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrown%20extensively%20in%20the%20Sindh%20region%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20these%20mangoes%20are%20known%20for%20their%20distinctively%20sweet%20and%20fragrant%20taste.%20Highly%20loved%20in%20both%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F128809%2Findia-pakistan-love-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20and%20Pakistan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20mangoes%20are%20large%20in%20size%20and%20have%20smooth%2C%20bright%20yellow%20skin.%20A%20favourite%20of%20many%2C%20it%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20fertile%20soil%20and%20warm%20climate%20of%20Sindh%20give%20them%20their%20distinctive%20taste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%20states%20that%20a%20Sindhri%20Mango%20can%20cost%20as%20high%20as%20Rs%203%2C000%20per%20piece.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsZaRk6OimB%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsZaRk6OimB%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_em