You%20can%20also%20add%20mango%2C%20banana%2C%20apples%2C%20berries%20to%20sweeten%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Divisha%20Jadhwani%2C%20a%20baby%20and%20child%20nutritionist.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20good%20option%20for%20Indian%20households%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290986%2Fhemapriya-natesan-sathumaavu-traditional-powder-for-babies-no-sugar-startup-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Esattu%20maavu%20%3C%2Fem%3E(multigrain)%20mix%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Most%20of%20these%20powders%20and%20mixes%20are%20sold%20by%20homegrown%20brands%20in%20case%20one%20can%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%20at%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20snacks%2C%20you%20could%20try%20%3Cem%3Emurmuras%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Emakhanas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20puffed%20%3Cem%3Erajgira%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20jowar%20puffs%2C%20ragi%20puffs%2C%20laddoos%2C%20and%20homemade%20cookies.%20All%20these%20can%20also%20be%20carried%20during%20travel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20a%20one%20week%20travel%20meal%20plan%20by%20Divisha%20Jadhwani-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2F2-23-1713781689.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2F2-23-1713781689.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2F2-23-1713781689-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2F2-23-1713781689-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2F2-23-1713781689-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2F2-23-1713781689-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20c