20because%20cold%20storage%20is%20a%20requirement%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346387%2Forganic-farmer-namakkal-tamil-nadu-hydroponics-maize-fodder-drip-irrigation-p-saravanan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindoor%20farming.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20often%20meet%20farmers%20and%20women%20who%20worked%20as%20helpers%20in%20fields.%20They%20had%20a%20tough%20time%20providing%20for%20their%20families%20and%20educating%20their%20women.%20I%20wanted%20to%20employ%20these%20women%20through%20whatever%20venture%20I%20began%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shubha%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20finally%20shortlisted%20mushrooms%20and%20saffron%20after%20months%20of%20research%20and%20feasibility%20studies%2C%20and%20decided%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20saffron.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20as%20%3Cem%3Ekesar%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Hindi%2C%20saffron%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20spices%20globally.%20Iran%20holds%20the%20title%20of%20the%20largest%20producer%20of%20saffron%2C%20with%20India%20following%20suit.%20Within%20India%2C%20this%20spice%20finds%20cultivation%20exclusively%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20owing%20to%20its%20favourable%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShubha%E2%80%99s%20son%20Ankit%20started%20researching%20ways%20to%20grow%20the%20spice%20indoors%20using%20aeroponics.%20He%20also%20looked%20into%20the%20technology%20and%20sensors%20needed%20to%20monitor%20the%20crop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaffron-1713440126-scaled.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20saffron%20is%20grown%20in%20a%20cold%20room%20in%20Mainpuri%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fup