0Kranti%20provides%20a%20new%20lease%20on%20life%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20of%20abuse%20left%20her%20traumatised%20with%20burning%20questions%20in%20her%20head.%20The%20question%20of%20%E2%80%9CWho%20deserves%20what%3F%E2%80%9D%20haunted%20her.%20She%20even%20attempted%20to%20end%20her%20life%20thrice%2C%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CI%20hated%20myself.%20I%20was%20vilified%20and%20shamed%20for%20my%20appearance%2C%20for%20where%20I%20came%20from%2C%20and%20made%20to%20believe%20that%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20deserve%20anything%20good%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reiterates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20change%20was%20on%20the%20horizon%20when%20she%20was%20in%20Class%2010%20and%20moved%20to%20Kerala%20with%20her%20parents.%20This%20was%20a%20new%20world%20for%20Sandhya%20%E2%80%94%20a%20world%20where%20no%20one%20knew%20the%20work%20her%20mother%20did%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20and%20finally%2C%20she%20could%20be%20free%20of%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Kerala%2C%20Sandhya%20failed%20to%20get%20admission%20into%20a%20private%20school%20as%20they%20had%20high%20cut-off%20marks.%20While%20she%20enjoyed%20studying%20and%20wanted%20to%20continue%20her%20education%2C%20the%20education%20system%20had%20traumatised%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20wanted%20to%20study%20psychology%20to%20%E2%80%9Cknow%20the%20answers%E2%80%9D%20about%20why%20people%20behave%20a%20certain%20way%20and%20who%20deserves%20what.%20She%20managed%20to%20secure%20admission%20to%20a%20Government%20school%20for%20Class%2011.%20Little%20did%20Sandhya%20know%20that%20her%20life%20would%20soon%20change%20forever%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20newspaper%20cutting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20revolution%20in%20a%20red%20light%20district%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20in%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%2C%20California-based%20Robin%20Chaurasiya%20started%20volunteering%20with%20NGOs%20across%20the%20world.%20In%202008%2C%20she%20worked%20with%20an%20N