20journey%20serves%20as%20a%20powerful%20lesson%20in%20resilience%2C%20showing%20everyone%20the%20significance%20of%20perseverance.%20His%20example%20shines%20light%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20celebrating%20failures%20and%20emphasising%20the%20qualities%20and%20skills%20honed%20throughout%20the%20journey%20%E2%80%94%20a%20practice%20that%20children%20and%20aspirants%20should%20embrace%2C%20just%20as%20Kunal%20did!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Feature%20Image%20Courtesy%20Kunal%20Virulkar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713352864000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347513%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kunal%20Virulkar%E2%80%99s%20post%20on%20X%20about%20not%20being%20selected%20for%20UPSC%20CSE%20celebrates%20the%20efforts%20of%20every%20aspirant.%20Here's%20why%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20support%20this%20narrative.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347513%2Fupsc-cse-result-kunal-virulkar-no-selection-x-twitter-viral-tweet-trending%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Raised%20By%20a%20Single%20Mom%2C%20Manipur%20Fighter%20Overcame%20Crushing%20Poverty%20to%20Become%20a%20Celebrated%20MMA%20Champion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%209%20March%2C%202024%2C%20Chungreng%20Koren%20%E2%80%94%20a%20mixed%20martial%20arts%20(MMA)%20fighter%20from%20Manipur%20also%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98The%20Indian%20Rhino%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20took%20his%20first%20step%20into%20the%20limelight%20at%20the%20Noida%20Indoor%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompeting%20in%20the%20co-main%20event%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290511%2Fanshul-jubli-road-to-ufc-best-indian-mma-fighter-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMatrix%20Fight%20Night%3C%2Fa%3E%20(MFN-14)%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20MMA%20promotion%2C%20Chungreng%20Koren%20took%20on%20veteran%20fighter%20Mohammed%20Farhad%20in%20a%20five-round%20fight%20for%20the%20(Interim)%20Bantamweight%20Title%20(61%20kg).%20As%20the%20fighters%20made%20their%20respective%20walk-ins%20to%20the%20octagon%2C%20the%2016%2C000-strong%20crowd%20at%20the%20Noida%20Indoor%20Stadium%20cheered%20in%20anticipation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20followed%20was%20a%20dominant%20performance%20by%20Chungreng%20who%20took%20the%20veteran%20fighter%20down%20at%20will%20with%20his%20relentless%20wrestling%20and%20then%20struck%20him%20with%20a%20barrage%20of%20ground-and-pound%20strikes%20till%20the%20referee%20intervened%20at%20the%20end%20of%20Round%204.%20Following%20the%20fight%2C%20with%20the%20belt%20wrapped%20around%20his%20shoulder%2C%20he%20made%20an%20appeal%20to%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20restore%20peace%20in%20Manipur%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20facing%20ethnic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20heartfelt%20appeal%20went%20viral%2C%20the%20moment%20also%20marked%20Chungreng%E2%80%99s%20emergence%20as%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20standout%20MMA%20fighters.%20When%20asked%20about%20the%20moment%20when%20he%20won%20the%20title%2C%20Chungreng%20says%20that%20he%20has%20no%20words%20to%20explain%20that%20feeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBrother%2C%20I%20worked%20so%20hard%20and%20overcame%20so%20much%20to%20be%20here%20now.%20Now%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I%E2%80%99m%20finding%20my%20way%20in%20this%20sport.%20Although%20this%20win%20is%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20my%20life%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20only%20getting%20started.%20When%20I%20recently%20went%20back%20home%2C%20I%20was%20so%20happy%20and%20surprised%20to%20see%20people%20greet%20me%20at%20the%20airport.%20My%20village%20came%20out%20to%20celebrate%20my%20success.%20Watching%20all%20this%20really%20warmed%20my%20heart.%20Now%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20back%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20to%20help%20my%20teammates%20a